}

###
# @name Delete meeting
DELETE {{NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL}}/meetings/{{meetingId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### ----------------- MEETING ATTENDEES ------------------

###
# @name List meeting attendees
